Top Recommended Courses

Mobile Application Pentesting & Bug Bounty Hunting in 2025 (Udemy): This comprehensive, hands-on course covers static and dynamic analysis, setting up a lab, using tools like Frida and Burp Suite, bypassing security controls, and writing effective reports.

The Complete Guide to Android Bug Bounty Penetration Tests (O'Reilly/Manning/CodeRedPro): This course provides step-by-step guidance on lab setup, information gathering, APK modification exploits, and exploiting specific vulnerabilities such as insecure authentication and data storage. It's suitable for bug bounty enthusiasts and developers.

Android Bug Bounty Hunting: Hunt Like a Rat (EC-Council): This program is designed to provide practical, hands-on skills in identifying, exploiting, and reporting vulnerabilities in mobile apps, covering topics from lab setup to advanced strategies.

Android Pentesting Bootcamp (Redfox Cybersecurity Academy): This live bootcamp offers hands-on training from setting up an environment to exploiting real-world vulnerabilities using tools like Frida, Burp Suite, and MobSF. It includes a certification option (CAAPT).

Mobile Application Penetration Testing (TCM Security): This course provides a solid foundation for continuing a career as a mobile application penetration tester and bug bounty hunter, covering common methodologies and practices.

